---
import Button from "./ui/Button.astro";
---

<section id="contact" class="py-16 md:py-32 bg-deep-charcoal relative scroll-mt-24">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10 max-w-4xl">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <span class="h-1 w-12 bg-viking-green"></span>
        <h2
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-light-cream"
        >
          Kontakt
        </h2>
        <span class="h-1 w-12 bg-viking-green"></span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Máte dotazy ohledně soutěže, registrace nebo partnerství? Neváhejte se
        ozvat.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact Card -->
    <div
      class="group category-card border-8 border-double border-viking-green/40 hover:border-viking-gold transition-colors duration-300 bg-deep-charcoal overflow-hidden"
    >
      <div class="contact-layout">
        <!-- Text side -->
        <div class="p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center gap-6 order-2 md:order-1">
          <div class="space-y-1">
            <h3
              class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display font-bold text-light-cream"
            >
              Marek Vidlář
            </h3>
            <p class="text-viking-gold font-display text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">
              Organizátor události
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            <p>Hlavní organizátor Slovanského Silového Klání.</p>
            <p>
              Pokud máte jakékoli otázky k soutěži, kategoriím, registraci nebo
              spolupráci, jsem tu pro vás.
            </p>
            <p>Rád zodpovím vše, co vás zajímá.</p>
          </div>

          <Button
            href="mailto:SlovanskeSiloveKlani@gmail.com"
            variant="primary"
            size="default"
            class="gap-2 w-max"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              class="size-5"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 19.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07-1.916V6.75"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            Napište mi
          </Button>
        </div>

        <!-- Photo side -->
        <div class="relative aspect-[4/3] md:aspect-auto order-1 md:order-2 overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src="/images/contact/marek-contact.avif"
            alt="Marek Vidlář — organizátor Slovanského Silového Klání"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-deep-charcoal/40 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contact-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .contact-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
